工果度連假都無請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上佢屋企見到仲有碗未洗<br />\n唉，蠢嘅人真係..."},{"pid":"e30a0e130fab297f8d762997ac529ded8c876604","tid":26261,"uid":524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T22:52:33.000Z","msg":"原來會咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依啲說話其實街邊啲人嗌交都一定聽到"},{"pid":"b0a6af705de41f72913d44afb525737479b6f2db","tid":26261,"uid":71041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"bdd466b4a1c5175f481f8809cedcd793f34b4d60","tid":26261,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T23:04:57.000Z","msg":"又bin垃圾新連登仔屍😂"},{"pid":"cf25d9c5a8eca7f6a8f2dee862125b7705c33e43","tid":26261,"uid":43853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T00:48:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔試下自辯"},{"pid":"72beca5a21b36c9d71247f59c4e00e8c1b0eaa34","tid":26261,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T00:59:04.000Z","msg":"抵死死廢老周街亂講野<br />\n祝你老豆入去俾人屌屎眼開年"},{"pid":"49c2983200b79d228bdc29602ac0aff2a2007b64","tid":26261,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪等佢係入面學下點收口囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢句真，樓主係學生哥根本冇能力打官司，夾硬打只會辛苦你自己(錢方面又係身心方面又係)你爸爸有做過倒不如今次好好反省下改善下脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7702b6d83a33b4e31f57e229e05ac9199e6ec8","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"個個犯完法搵律師就唔使坐監，監房就唔會咁多人啦。等5個月佢就出黎架啦，坐監無咩野架咋，玩下玩下就一日，5個月好易過的。<br />\n<br />\n你老豆點都要受點教訓架啦"},{"pid":"33bc296b98b924f7e6ed88b61d38208a4a18bb75","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢認左就好難搞，況且8個月好似唔係要坐足，而佢咁大個人幫得佢幾次?等佢知驚仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實坐5個月"},{"pid":"958f7eab53fd2ee296bed5cb30a1242eff295da0","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男人老狗做左咪認囉 坐下反省下咪幾好<br />\n下下做完又要驚 女人咩家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人都係人 冇special case <br />\n佢都認左你就由佢啦 乜都幫果啲叫愚孝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知係佢錯，<br />\n我一直都好憎佢，咁事到如今都想睇下有冇咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我自己覺得8個月係咪有啲重？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要做既野係每次拜山時買多些日用品比佢，等佢好捱d.<br />\n<br />\n利申：坐過好多監房"},{"pid":"756050f9d43e74d4ad886a2073268f8c7c415057","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刑事恐嚇咁大罪,根本點都唔應該認啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都驚係咪比差佬水，叫佢認左佢就無咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心，一定係，這是差佬日常工作之一，只怪你老豆蠢，差佬都信。"},{"pid":"3081eb93f2aedba8288cf75df20b36924df51395","tid":26261,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我半桶水答你，應左 係無得 maan...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上訴刑期唔係唔得 但你有無份判詞？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無啊，件事太突然問佢既機會都無</blockquote><br />\n八個月算重刑期，究竟佢做左d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實說，我都唔肯定佢做左咩，問佢又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地響朵 + 刑事恐嚇 都係坐三個月<br />\n<br />\n恐嚇小販管理主任男子被判入獄<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199903/31/0331065.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F199903%2F31%2F0331065.htm&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=422d5ae1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199903/31/0331065.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a3915867b9d23eb9e49c0608489b93cb59f6c1b2","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半年唔洗出返黎，將請律師果幾千蚊買煙比佢食下算啦，1千蚊10包，每一個月幫佢買1千都幾舒服架啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劃飛？你邊個監房咁貴？赤柱都無咁貴bor"},{"pid":"e76e16fc0ec6cc75198d2741c47f6b0b44e14135","tid":26261,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你俾佢喺入面8個月反省下自己呢世人做過d乜, 出反黎個人會和順左, 勤力左, 正氣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有8個月時間俾佢減肥, 降低患心臟病同糖尿病的機會, 成件事冇壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係為佢好就唔好再揾佢啦, 佢都要尊嚴架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一聽就知你坐個，師兄咩Number?"},{"pid":"257b287e8e86afde8b10154ed28c55cfb97769e7","tid":26261,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"等佢坐下監 唔好哂錢"},{"pid":"937b16bba091d55f7e86fd27089226ee5d7371d7","tid":26261,"uid":65001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"唔識依d 不過幫你推一推"},{"pid":"d0a695d751505379804d469322e627da2e3cfbd3","tid":26261,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:50:13.000Z","msg":"Binc 先"},{"pid":"18e519f13a8de3cd7c641a4990a6f33f08206ab6","tid":26261,"uid":66442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"巴打，呢個時候試試揾區議員"},{"pid":"b66afe7da100712691eb54281c385ce132e545a8","tid":26261,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b25146a91b71588abc67684c0f4f5d2abc40d97c","tid":26261,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f47fe159c789457bfc9d4f6a0f7037801bcd511","tid":26261,"uid":21717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:04:18.000Z","msg":"恐嚇人，自己受返個後果"},{"pid":"b6bbe713522e84451e0b0fffda29dcf2e41a9aa2","tid":26261,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"講句野就坐5個月會唔會太重啊"},{"pid":"424428d0525da6cf41cb0f1caaaf057eb356b469","tid":26261,"uid":31901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人諗野都唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad47f83a8818593138042e890c251f873560416","tid":26261,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講句野就坐5個月會唔會太重啊</blockquote><br />\n\t<br />\n肯定無咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n人地響朵 + 刑事恐嚇 都係坐三個月<br />\n<br />\n恐嚇小販管理主任男子被判入獄<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199903/31/0331065.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F199903%2F31%2F0331065.htm&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=422d5ae1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199903/31/0331065.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b2a4727b160b9cb2418c95708b36b6afd9c51fb2","tid":26261,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"不如咁啦<br />\n你去問下法援先<br />\n如果佢地叫你唔好晒錢<br />\n咁你就放手啦<br />\n可能好似上面巴打咁講<br />\n坐8個月可能會改過晒呢<br />\nBtw 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bba244ef057dfc7570c3badf2a46d075cb9022","tid":26261,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"坐完八個月未又係一個好漢<br />\n扣埋假期半年可以見番你"},{"pid":"5a192bdaf8adb24164585310935bb9e4f820a479","tid":26261,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"判左la woo，你可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接搵律師la一定要"},{"pid":"b322a3456ab1f6ba33ce466378f7829562b22e7e","tid":26261,"uid":35160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"你老豆咁撚火爆 把口又唔收 <br />\n你探佢仲可以屌返你轉頭<br />\n成件事自己攞黎 你就唔好理喇 <br />\n而且全緊 你都冇野好做 當比個教訓佢<br />\n佢都唔緊 你緊黎做咩"},{"pid":"47a95653387c7c9c987c7be58942580a95890f34","tid":26261,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478bc39173a776b8a064308264ac0a693b65c7a5","tid":26261,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"題外話:勿盡信網友意見<br />\n當中唔少係查緊案既警察會不斷留言叫你認罪，曾經我屋企上網比鄰舍用嚟做犯法野，去旅行翻香港比警察扣留左我40個鐘<br />\n保釋期間上網問左好多所謂有法律知識既人<br />\n佢地會一面倒話你講大話，有咩留翻同大老爺講啦，認罪啦，無架啦無得打，自己做過咩自己知啦，一早認有得減刑等等說話<br />\n最後比左少少錢律師同我去搞續保同錄口供<br />\n保釋左一年之後警方同我講無條件釋放我，事情告一段落<br />\n法律依家野唔好上網問，如果我當初信鳩班人我諗應該有排坐 <br />\n同埋一堆話認罪個d無得打既人真係好無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11af0aa0ff19239ebf409d24b08df737522eb89","tid":26261,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"俾個case你參考下，首先我本身職業經常要同律師有來往，所以就會同佢地比較熟，早幾年我細佬刑事恐嚇，情況大鑊過你老豆而家（如果你老豆冇呃你），當時情況大概係，我細佬飲醉咗，有𠝹刀，有推黑警，cctv影晒。<br />\n<br />\n嗰時我立即向我d律師朋友求救，之後就向主控官方面攞證供同cctv(過程唔係好記得，因為太耐），點知一睇cctv就知大鑊，嗰時律師勸我細佬認罪，因為認罪個官就唔會睇晒所有cctv(點解唔睇晒cctv我真係唔記得，因為推黑警係cctv最後部分），最後我律師朋友轉介咗單case俾佢相熟，專打刑事案件嘅同行。<br />\n<br />\n之後求情信，悔意，應承個官戒酒同埋上戒酒課程（呢單case個求情點係飲醉酒先會鬧事），最後罰咗幾千，唔記得有冇案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n埋單朋友價都要80000幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n##當值律師係廢嘅，hea做<br />\n<br />\n##當時係佔中前，反對派正值日益擴張之時，我細佬俾人拉嘅時候戇尻尻自爆係某反對派嘅支持者，之後個黑警同我細佬講，大sir話一定要做撚死佢&hellip;&hellip;如果當時冇律師或搵當值律師，我細佬入梗<br />\n<br />\n##你老豆單case，一係佢有好多嘢隱瞞你，一係對方係公職人員，如果唔係一般打咀炮嘅刑事恐嚇唔會咁嚴重判8個月<br />\n<br />\n最後，你自己決定點做啦⋯⋯但你如果冇d錢，呢個遊戲根本冇得玩，祝你好運！！"},{"pid":"0cec96dfd4678ffa3e5bf5799321c288c86975d3","tid":26261,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"路過幫推"},{"pid":"63813de9a67d46d5588794edb9be5100474511a8","tid":26261,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以講下成件事係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf13a0e04aac3c0bd722d38bdf94ad7dbde26ce","tid":26261,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恐嚇人，自己受返個後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同"},{"pid":"64baba5bd675d67158254001da54be5d4b6c1648","tid":26261,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"要小心鬼拿奇"},{"pid":"35e46f43b9abf91e835159b305fc293b609cd2dc","tid":26261,"uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"認左就算啦<br />\n學下收口<br />\n唔好以為咩人都得罪得<br />\n你仲要窮 係法律面前真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f27f86a43a84bf9bba0cef99d4b3b1aed02ec2f","tid":26261,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"認咗好難搞<br />\n上訴萬一唔得仲西<br />\n最重要係無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc5391b00a5c2dd33989aecf864a15ec7e473b7","tid":26261,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:34:49.000Z","msg":"見樓主似真心同孝順...<br />\n<br />\n第一，認咗罪唔係話無得搞，而係成本會高好多<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔好話咩講咗一句嘢就要判八個月好誇張。自稱三合會都係一句嘢、喺飛機上亂噏有詐彈都係一句嘢，你試吓三更半夜幾個大隻佬圍著你講見你一穫打你一穫，你覺得係唔係恐嚇丫<br />\n<br />\n巴打係有孝心嘅，探多啲監好過啦，俾你搞一輪刑期減半4個月，搞得嚟都差唔多放監"},{"pid":"b671bdd2fc6e850ab1e2e9d548eadc6eb13f63a4","tid":26261,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話:勿盡信網友意見<br />\n當中唔少係查緊案既警察會不斷留言叫你認罪，曾經我屋企上網比鄰舍用嚟做犯法野，去旅行翻香港比警察扣留左我40個鐘<br />\n保釋期間上網問左好多所謂有法律知識既人<br />\n佢地會一面倒話你講大話，有咩留翻同大老爺講啦，認罪啦，無架啦無得打，自己做過咩自己知啦，一早認有得減刑等等說話<br />\n最後比左少少錢律師同我去搞續保同錄口供<br />\n保釋左一年之後警方同我講無條件釋放我，事情告一段落<br />\n法律依家野唔好上網問，如果我當初信鳩班人我諗應該有排坐 <br />\n同埋一堆話認罪個d無得打既人真係好無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad349362e23f6b98c2bea47905fe5b8e861d9e0c","tid":26261,"uid":45884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"你老豆認咩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一開始請當值律師都唔洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5f1ef45304d232cb7e8a0c937a1c62fecf3a18","tid":26261,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"法律嘢望落好遠，但其實隨時就身陷險境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲錢真係唔慳得<br />\n<br />\n律師同醫生都係攞正旗號搶你錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681b3ef17c197ac839681327d2817ee019e7df12","tid":26261,"uid":9520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d71f6095268910f46487d5f8c4ca612e7763faae","tid":26261,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"下次認罪都要搵律師，冇律師你自己on99認比人砌都砌撚惡"},{"pid":"c8b6d263b83095270e60c894339a4950d0cbebd4","tid":26261,"uid":36607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"你阿爸認左罪，就定罪上訴似乎無乜可能，所以上訴刑期比較實際。<br />\n<br />\n法援方面，要通過經濟同案情審查。經濟審查係指你阿爸資產唔可以過$290,380 (至於點計法你真係諗住上訴再講)；<br />\n<br />\n至於案情審查，你阿爸要有合理嘅上訴理據，「判刑明顯過重」係一個常見並且有力嘅法律理據，但係八個月刑期是否明顯過重，有好多因素要睇，例如你阿爸有無類似定罪記錄、犯案性質、你阿爸年紀同經濟負擔等。不過認罪本身已經係刑期扣減嘅最大因素（一般為刑罰嘅三份一）。<br />\n<br />\n所以要上訴刑期，你要睇番未扣減認罪嘅刑期，係咪過重，呢層就要睇案例，你真係有需要我可以幫你睇下。<br />\n<br />\n如果想知申請法援詳情，你去<a href=\"http://www.lad.gov.hk/chi/las/criminal/ec.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lad.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Flas%2Fcriminal%2Fec.html&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=27a1b983\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lad.gov.hk/chi/las/criminal/ec.html</a> 睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩想知再講，不過最後做乜決定都好，應該由你阿爸決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：考緊pcll，純粹個人睇法，並非法律意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4af576cffbf6704090a7b182bdee26e9c8305d","tid":26261,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"你試下搵低褲超人或者區議員？？"},{"pid":"3322422db98f39ecc8095f30fc76a84a8547c526","tid":26261,"uid":17585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"打感動"},{"pid":"42f049b527654982f0972fc7a0ad3239232678b6","tid":26261,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"區議員 通常有提供 免費法律意見<br />\n<br />\n試下囉"},{"pid":"0a75ff0dddef216e7abf57967891128a547ec471","tid":26261,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你阿爸認左罪，就定罪上訴似乎無乜可能，所以上訴刑期比較實際。<br />\n<br />\n法援方面，要通過經濟同案情審查。經濟審查係指你阿爸資產唔可以過$290,380 (至於點計法你真係諗住上訴再講)；<br />\n<br />\n至於案情審查，你阿爸要有合理嘅上訴理據，「判刑明顯過重」係一個常見並且有力嘅法律理據，但係八個月刑期是否明顯過重，有好多因素要睇，例如你阿爸有無類似定罪記錄、犯案性質、你阿爸年紀同經濟負擔等。不過認罪本身已經係刑期扣減嘅最大因素（一般為刑罰嘅三份一）。<br />\n<br />\n所以要上訴刑期，你要睇番未扣減認罪嘅刑期，係咪過重，呢層就要睇案例，你真係有需要我可以幫你睇下。<br />\n<br />\n如果想知申請法援詳情，你去<a href=\"http://www.lad.gov.hk/chi/las/criminal/ec.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lad.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Flas%2Fcriminal%2Fec.html&d=JusVMO8o1agBzVcejjMw%2B5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=27a1b983\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.lad.gov.hk/chi/las/criminal/ec.html</a> 睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩想知再講，不過最後做乜決定都好，應該由你阿爸決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：考緊pcll，純粹個人睇法，並非法律意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係好似過左 14日 time limit? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攞 extension 要 show good cause threshold 應該幾高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bcf4634bd71eb8022f429805218d0d058f4be4","tid":26261,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"上網班撚樣真係唔好信"},{"pid":"0bb9efada171491c907ae0c251c981709bf0701c","tid":26261,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"Cap 227 s 114 Procedure for appeals under section 113 prior to entry of appeal<br />\n<br />\nWhere a person is authorized by section 113 to appeal to a judge, the following provisions shall apply-<br />\n<br />\n(a)\tthe appellant shall, within 14 days after the day of his conviction or the order or determination by the magistrate or within such extended time as may be ordered upon application made in accordance with section 114A, give to the magistrates' clerk notice in writing of his appeal, stating the general grounds of his appeal, and signed by him or his agent on his behalf, and thereupon the magistrates' clerk shall give a copy of such notice to the respondent and, if he is not the respondent, also to the Secretary for Justice; (See Forms 101, 102) (Amended 6 of 1968 s. 3)<br />\n(b)\twhen a notice of appeal has been given to the magistrates' clerk the magistrate whose conviction, order or determination is the subject of the notice of appeal shall prepare a signed statement of his findings on the facts and other grounds of his decision and within 15 days after the day on which the notice of appeal was given cause a copy to be served upon the appellant and respondent and, if he is not the respondent, also upon the Secretary for Justice; (Amended 6 of 1968 s. 3)<br />\n(c)\t(Repealed 13 of 1995 s. 65)<br />\n<br />\n(Replaced 24 of 1949 s. 39. Amended L.N. 362 of 1997)<br />\n[cf. 1933 c. 38 s. 1 U.K.]<br />\n<br />\nCap 227 s 114A Extension of time for giving notice of appeal under section 114<br />\n<br />\n(1)\tWhere it appears to a magistrate or to a judge, on application made in accordance with subsection (2), that any person wishing to appeal against any conviction, order or determination by any magistrate has failed to give the notice of appeal required by section 114 within the period of 14 days prescribed by paragraph (a) thereof, the magistrate or the judge, as the case may be, may, on good cause being shown by the applicant, order that such notice may be given within such further time as shall be specified in such order.<br />\n(2)\tAn application un"},{"pid":"5ff8ff13969dcb2e697a0067433c5ea11a9b0afc","tid":26261,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網班撚樣真係唔好信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，搵律師最實際 好多人無奶過野上嚟鳩up扮大狀衝出嚟柒"},{"pid":"4c8fe960f8610156e85aa0e452b18cb3137222ba","tid":26261,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:49:54.000Z","msg":"入去八個月學下控制情緒"},{"pid":"a560f4cd1e56022838e9074b10ad529028a7ad59","tid":26261,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"樓主你肯定係刑事恐嚇？<br />\n一般criminal intimidation 唔會8個月咁重喎<br />\n<br />\n利申： trainee solicitor <br />\n建議你搵律師 <br />\n唔好聽連登仔9 up"},{"pid":"03f3623981e7db753d661843a991f0d9bfb15176","tid":26261,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"8個月啫"}]}